replies.body:
Sadly that wouldn't work! ;_;

Because you play on EUNE, you can't use cards purchased from Austria or Germany since both of those regions are tied to EUW, and RP cards can't be transferred between servers. That being said, Czech Republic should have prepaid cards available for purchase, along with some other payment methods on the list we have [** over here**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/203701590).

If you're having a hard time finding prepaid cards for sale anywhere, you could always try one of the other options. I'd suggest Paysafe myself since it's really reliable, but if you have more questions you should definitely consider ticketing our Billing team [**right here**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new ). They have even more info! :)
